<div style="position:absolute;top:3.12in;left:1.92in;width:5.23in;line-height:0.25in;"><span style="font-style:normal;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:DejaVu Sans Condensed;color:#000000">AVANT DE CLASSER VOTRE CONTRAT, LISEZ-LE ATTENTIVEMENT</span><span style="font-style:normal;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:DejaVu Sans Condensed;color:#000000"> </span><br></div>
